channel.title: No clients load on my PC
channel.description:
I've never had trouble with clients before, but every time I try to load a client it pops up and the screen just stays white, it doesn't load or anything, I've tried installing the new version of java, I've restarted my computer a few times, Don't say it's my variables, cause it's not. I've tried loading all the clients on my computer, none work.
Can someone please offer me some help/advice?
Thanks,
Jayden.
Edit: I can't even load runescape..
